headline: Warner Bros. Discovery Announces Conference Participation for the Month of September
summary: Warner Bros. Discovery, Inc. (Nasdaq: WBD) today announced that its President and CEO David Zaslav and its Chief Financial Officer Gunnar Wiedenfels will present at conferences during the month of September.
